text: The NWA Oriental Tag Team Championship was a professional wrestling tag team championship recognized by the National Wrestling Alliance through its partnership with the Korean Pro Wrestling Association. == Title history == == See also == * List of National Wrestling Alliance championships * NWA Oriental Heavyweight Championship == References == == External links == * Wrestling- Titles.com Category:National Wrestling Alliance championships Category:Tag team wrestling championships Category:Recurring sporting events established in 1982 Category:Recurring events disestablished in 2004
